BOXER NIGEL BENN CHARGED WITH GRIEVOUS BODILY HARM . British boxer Nigel Benn was charged with grievous bodily harm on Thursday after an incident at a London nightclub in September , police said . The 32 - year - old super - middleweight boxer , who announced his retirement from the ring last week , is to spend the night in police custody before appearing before magistrates on Friday , police added . Benn , who retired after being beaten by Irishman Steve Collins in a WBO title challenge , ended his boxing career with a record of 48 fights , 42 wins , one draw and five defeats . 
